:magnifyPanel:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/ab.handbook
Custom Magnification

Hold down SELECT to drag the slider to
the desired numeric value (displayed
in the Magnification Percentage field).

Click SELECT on either side of the
slider control to increase or decrease
magnification in increments of 1%.

Then click SELECT on Apply (to set the
new magnification) or Reset (to return
to the previous setting).

#
:magnifySlider:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/ab.handbook
Custom Magnification

Hold down SELECT to drag the slider to the
desired numeric value (displayed in the
Magnify Page field).

Or click SELECT on either side of the slider
control to increase or decrease magnification
in increments of 1%.

Then click SELECT on Apply (to set this 
magnification) or Reset (to return to previous
setting).

